{"tid":2486780,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"40歲移民英國500萬點投資創被動收入｜龔成教室","createTime":"2021-04-13T06:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T02:10:09.000Z","uid":358086,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6faaa5658a68100951eb6a637ac9dd09357627","tid":2486780,"uid":358086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:13:36.000Z","msg":"40歲8月一家四口移民英國、賣樓套500萬點投資創被動收入｜龔成教室<br />\n<br />\n2021.04.11 by 龔成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQEGhnQiuSWRvHheM3egeL9jTk6twW7DHfCaMeqcznUNp?filename=WToeOi1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWToeOi1.png&h=0e85714e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n40歲讀者打算8月一家四口移民英國，現放售自住樓，約可套現670萬現金，再買一層約170萬港幣的英國樓，因怕到英國後短時間內難找到工作，想知如何運用賣樓後約500萬現金投資創被動收入？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>理財個案｜讀者來信：40歲8月一家四口移民英國 </strong><br />\n<br />\n你好老師，本人40歲，打算8月一家四口移民英國，浪費了之前的增值資產的機會，一路都沒有買股票只儲現金。現在放售香港層樓之後，大概總共有670萬現金，已準備買一層大約170萬港幣的英國樓。餘下大約500萬的現金應該甚樣分配和部署製做被動收入，應該投資香港股票或是英國股票，和怕到英國短時間內都難找到工作。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>應投資香港股票或是英國股票？ </strong><br />\n<br />\n想問問你的股票班對在英國買股票有幫助嗎？都是差不多道理嗎？<br />\n<br />\n和你的咁多本書之中，我應該選擇邊本開始讀？<br />\n<br />\n謝謝你<br />\n<br />\n<strong>龔成老師分析：可投資平穩增長港股</strong> <br />\n<br />\n你可以建立一個平衡的財富組合，你40歲，仍是財富有增長的年齡，因此可投資平穩增長股。另外，相信長遠港股仍不差的，你可以投資港股，如對英國股票有認識，就小部分投資英國股票。$500萬，暫時建議你留一半現金，到你安頓好，先慢慢動用，建立組合。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新舊經濟各類股都要有 </strong><br />\n<br />\n我哋最重要是建立一個長期的「財富組合」，要優質，要平衡，要適合你的年齡與風險承受程度，新舊經濟各類股都要有。同一行業不能太多，同一股不能太多。<br />\n<br />\n要平衡，建立後長期持有，不是買賣賺差價，而是成為你財富組合一部分。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">港股推介： <br />\n<br />\n港股，你可以考慮盈富（<a href=\"http://2800.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F2800.HK&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=65ac804c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">2800.HK</a>）、銀娛（<a href=\"http://0027.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0027.HK&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=1720393c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0027.HK</a>）、恒基（<a href=\"http://0012.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0012.HK&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=81c7e387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0012.HK</a>）、港鐵（<a href=\"http://0066.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0066.HK&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=5eff0274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0066.HK</a>）、平安（<a href=\"http://2318.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F2318.HK&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=ec326b8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">2318.HK</a>）、粵海（<a href=\"http://0270.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0270.HK&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=8cb7ef36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0270.HK</a>）、領展（<a href=\"http://0823.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0823.HK&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=664f82f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0823.HK</a>）、希慎（<a href=\"http://0014.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0014.HK&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=2e1cede8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0014.HK</a>）、太古地產（<a href=\"http://1972.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1972.HK&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=72ee1356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">1972.HK</a>）等，你可以了解下這些股票，然後從中選股。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美股可考慮投資ETF 如VOO</strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，你可以同時考慮美股，都可以的，最簡單投資ETF，如VOO，這是最好的選擇。至於我的股票班，所教的是價值投資法，即是巴菲特用的方法，你投資港股、美股、英國股票，都適用，不過課堂以港股為例解說，你就要自行調整。<br />\n<br />\n至於我的書，在三聯、商務、誠品都有得賣。由於部分書在一些書店已斷，所以若你見唔到，問下職員就得（又或向職員訂都可以）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.businesstimes.com.hk/articles/132780/%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A1%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-40%E6%AD%B28%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E5%9B%9B%E5%8F%A3%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-%E8%B3%A3%E6%A8%93%E5%A5%97500%E8%90%AC%E9%BB%9E%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%89%B5%E8%A2%AB%E5%8B%95%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5-%E9%BE%94%E6%88%90?fbclid=IwAR22iwQrJqH-EKU4XIyBxQAFEtdUg2Ze5qhZhzJrbOmNZK16_T0sJlBk918#utm_source=Facebook&amp;utm_medium=page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstimes.com.hk%2Farticles%2F132780%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588-40%25E6%25AD%25B28%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25A5%2597500%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2585%25A5-%25E9%25BE%2594%25E6%2588%2590%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR22iwQrJqH-EKU4XIyBxQAFEtdUg2Ze5qhZhzJrbOmNZK16_T0sJlBk918%23utm_source%3DFacebook%26utm_medium%3Dpage&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=14f1f741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.businesstimes.com.hk/articles/132780/%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A1%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-40%E6%AD%B28%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E5%9B%9B%E5%8F%A3%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-%E8%B3%A3%E6%A8%93%E5%A5%97500%E8%90%AC%E9%BB%9E%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%89%B5%E8%A2%AB%E5%8B%95%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5-%E9%BE%94%E6%88%90?fbclid=IwAR22iwQrJqH-EKU4XIyBxQAFEtdUg2Ze5qhZhzJrbOmNZK16_T0sJlBk918#utm_source=Facebook&amp;utm_medium=page</a>"},{"pid":"c2aa8420549e26f60b7c8b9fbd51af5fa30f65e5","tid":2486780,"uid":358086,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:15:30.000Z","msg":"去到英國都係買2800<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5325d559ebaa5449395458fbac4102968870e279","tid":2486780,"uid":156336,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"仲買港股<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d76f3a44870047125b76b34c81a8d1a3712e22","tid":2486780,"uid":26976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"我根本無貨"},{"pid":"a980c0e9531cdf7a68da794fc83cc42a51f